show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/UUgE2a
show.description: Soumya was deeply love to her husband, Bharath so much so that she was willing to do anything for him. Blinded by love, she never questioned his actions. But Bharath, a master manipulator and a seasoned artist in real life, led a secret life that Soumya knew nothing about. He kept a close eye on her 24/7 not out of love, but to ensure he could carry out his shady dealings without being caught. Behind her back, Bharath was involved with multiple women and engaged in various illegal activities. When Soumya finally uncovers the truth, the question arises will she take revenge, or will she walk away in silence? And what will become of Bharath once his double life is exposed?
